longBusinessSummary: Maha Energy AB (publ) engages in the exploration, development, and production of crude oil and natural gas in Brazil, the United States, and Oman. It owns 65% working interest in the Block 70 project located in Oman; and 98.41% working interest in the light oil Illinois Basin property located in Illinois, the United States. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
